column5: Hey guys was planning on hitting the Niagara area tomorrow morn for lakers, browns and bows but its impossible to find someone to go out with on the week days. Since ill be goin solo am gonna drop the boat in at the rivers off cooks for crappy and perch> does anyone know how its been? Are the launches in keswick free of ice?
LAUNCH IN BRADFORD.....no ice , fish seem to be there from other posts..good luck
